# Copy to server/.env. Provider calls are made in-process (adr-007) — set a
# key per provider you want routable; models whose provider has no key fail
# instantly and the routing walk moves on.

# Free-tier MVP keys (the default routes in routing.ts run on these):
GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...
GEMINI_API_KEY=...

# Optional paid fallbacks / BYOK providers:
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# Local Ollama (dev-only gemma3-4b fallback); default shown:
# OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434/v1

# Operator-cost guardrails (adr-008); defaults shown, 0 disables one.
# BYOK requests are exempt — they spend the caller's key.
# LIMIT_GENERATIONS_PER_DAY=10
# LIMIT_REGENERATIONS_PER_DAY=30
# LIMIT_BACKGROUNDS_PER_DAY=3
# DAILY_BUDGET_USD=5

# PORT=3001
